author: mprudhom
msg: Added a 'java14.jar' property that can be used to specify the location of the JDK 1.4 runtime jar, against which we will compile the JDK 1.4-specific modules. This can be used to ensure that JDK 1.5-specific methods and classes don't slip into the JDK 1.4 modules.
